X-Men: Days of Future Past;;91;;90;;PG-13;;Convinced that mutants pose a threat to humanity, Dr. Bolivar Trask (Peter Dinklage) develops the Sentinels, enormous robotic weapons that can detect a mutant gene and zero in on that person. In the 21st century, the Sentinels have evolved into highly efficient killing machines. With mutants now facing extinction, Wolverine (Hugh Jackman) volunteers to go back in time and rally the X-Men of the past to help change a pivotal moment in history and thereby save their future.;;Fantasy,Sci-fi,Adventure,Action;;Bryan Singer;;2014;;Hugh Jackman,James McAvoy,Michael Fassbender,Jennifer Lawrence,Halle Berry,Elliot Page,Peter Dinklage,Ian McKellen,Patrick Stewart,Anna Paquin,Evan Peters,Nicholas Hoult,Josh Helman,Evan Jonigkeit,Lucas Till,Omar Sy,Fan Bingbing,Daniel Cudmore,Shawn Ashmore,Adan Canto;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/x_men_days_of_future_past